the twisted son of a bitch who got away.

598
00:44:21,760 --> 00:44:24,956
So, who is
the twisted son of a bitch?

599
00:44:26,081 --> 00:44:27,667
I call him the trinity killer.

600
00:44:28,905 --> 00:44:30,044
Kills in threes.

601
00:44:30,429 --> 00:44:32,546
Been doing it all over the country
for years.

602
00:44:32,877 --> 00:44:35,177
Problem is, I can't prove he exists.

603
00:44:35,667 --> 00:44:37,953
