doesn't talk to each other.

604
00:44:38,546 --> 00:44:40,805
So no one at the FBI
is even on board.

605
00:44:42,432 --> 00:44:43,474
Just me.

606
00:44:44,056 --> 00:44:46,471
I've been looking for a break.
Then this happens.

607
00:44:46,596 --> 00:44:47,596
Lisa Bell.

608
00:44:48,146 --> 00:44:50,946
Her murder profile
