00:47:39,051 --> 00:47:41,201
Big plans this evening, sergeant?

643
00:47:41,840 --> 00:47:43,440
The usual, lieutenant.

644
00:47:57,105 --> 00:47:58,105
Hey, guys.

645
00:48:00,252 --> 00:48:01,252
