677
00:52:07,546 --> 00:52:09,215
<i>Maybe tonight wasn't perfect.</i>

678
00:52:09,340 --> 00:52:12,133
<i>Maybe I need to reboot
the way I do things.</i>

679
00:52:15,599 --> 00:52:17,625
<i>But at least I'm on the right road.</i>

680
00:52:18,959 --> 00:52:21,384
